:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">E</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">qual </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">P</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">ay information</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> and address findings</span></li><li style="font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 29.6pt; padding-left:6.4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Resourcing (staff and funding) to support p</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">articipation in Athena SWAN at institutional and departmental levels (+ </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">development and implementation of </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">related </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">action plans)</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span></li></ul><ul type="circle" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 29.6pt; padding-left:6.4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Leadership and succession p</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">lanning programmes and </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">senior engagement activities</span></li><li style="font-family:'Courier New'; font-size:11pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 29.6pt; padding-left:6.4pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Public commitment to equality and diversity</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">, spe</span><span style="font-fami